shingle fan
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a broad slope of loose angular stones that have been washed down by water action between hillsides.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
See:fan
